         </div>
         <div type="edition" ana="#b1" subtype="transcription" xml:id="squf0002.transcription" corresp="#squf0002.diplomatic #squf0002.translation">
            <p>θάρσ<supplied reason="undefined">ει</supplied>
               <lb/>
                    Σωφ<lb break="no"/>όνι <lb/>
               <expan><abbr>ἐτ</abbr><ex>ῶν</ex></expan> <num value="40">μ᾽</num></p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="squf0002.translation" corresp="#squf0002.diplomatic #squf0002.transcription">
            <p> Be of good courage, Sophonios! Forty years old. </p>
         </div>
      <div type="edition" subtype="transcription_segmented"><p><w xml:id="squf0002-1" xml:lang="grc">θάρσ<supplied reason="undefined">ει</supplied></w> <w xml:id="squf0002-2" xml:lang="grc">Σωφόνι</w> <w xml:id="squf0002-3" xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>ἐτ</abbr><ex>ῶν</ex></expan></w> <num xml:id="squf0002-4" value="40" xml:lang="grc">μ᾽</num></p>
</div>
</body>
      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>This is a complete tombstone inscription. It opens with the standard Greek "Be of good courage," followed by the name and age of the deceased. Dimensions given are for entire stone, not just inscribed area.</p>
